<h2> Adding a question</h2>
<form method="POST" action="/add">
	
	Add a question: <input type = "text" name = "question"/>
	Add an answer: <input type = "text" name = "answer"/>
	Add an explaination <input type = "text" name = "explaination"/>
	<input type = "submit" value = "Submit to database!"/>
</form>
{{#if submitted}}
	Thanks for contributing to the question bank!
	<br>
	Feel free to add more, or if you're ready, take the <a href="questions">quiz</a>!
{{/if}}